{{Han compound|辵|斤|ls=psc|alt1=辶|c1=s|c2=p|t1=walk}} – to be near something.

===Etymology===
{{zh-ref|Karlgren (1933)}} relates {{och-l|近}} to {{och-l|幾|id=1|imminent}}.

{{och-l|近|id=2|to come near to; to approach}} is the [[exoactive]]/[[causative]] derivation of {{och-l|近|id=1|to be near}} ({{zh-ref|Schuessler, 2007}}).

Compare {{cog|mkh-vie-pro|*t-kəɲ}}, whence {{cog|vi|gần||near}}.

